### Additional Flags
You can append these flags to any of the above commands to fine-tune the system:
- `--frame-skip`: Skip N frames to save CPU (default is 3). Example: `--frame-skip 5`
- `--persistence`: Number of consecutive frames required to trigger alert (default is 5). Example: `--persistence 3`
- `--conf`: Confidence threshold for the YOLO model (default is 0.25). Example: `--conf 0.5`